                            <comment id="13135325" author="jdcryans" created="Tue, 25 Oct 2011 18:47:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Shouldn&apos;t the defaults in the code be changed too? Stuff like this in HConstants:&lt;/p&gt;

